WEBVTT

00:00,000 --> 00:04,950
From Idea To Execution

00:05,000 --> 00:09,950
The hidden cost in most programs is rework created by weak under handoffs.

00:10,000 --> 00:14,950
Make the decision rule visible so project leads can apply it consistently.

00:15,000 --> 00:19,950
Start with one checkpoint, one owner, and one weekly metric tied to actually.

00:20,000 --> 00:24,950
Teams ship with less friction when decisions and reinforcement happen in the same rhythm.

00:25,000 --> 00:29,950
Start small, document what changed, and promote only patterns that hold under pressure.
